        <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
            <head>Biographical Note</head>
            <p><!-- BIOGHIST REQUIRED -->Consultant specializing in management and educational systems. Edelman (A.B., 1924, M.S. School of Engineering, 1926) was particularly active in the National Security Industrial Association, the National Defense Education Institute, and Electronic Industries Association.</p>
            <p/>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>Correspondence, notes, memoranda, and reports of Edelman. The papers reflect his involvements with the organizations above as well as his activities as a consultant to a number of government agencies and industrial concerns.</p>
            <p/>
        </scopecontent>
